<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Mars</title>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <%= csp_meta_tag %>

    <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/fc19e69a08.js"></script>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="jumbotron jumbotron-fluid">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="display-4">LIFE ON MARS</h1>
          <p class="lead">Come join our New Martian Community</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row feature text-center">
      <div class="col-12 col-sm">
        <h3>Wide Open Terrain</h3>
        <br />
          <p>Plenty of acreage for your desert ranch or beach front property! You read that right - after years of reshaping, Mars now has it's very own ocean! <p>
            <img src="" class="rounded">
      </div>

      <div class="col-12 col-sm">
        <h3>Reliable Atmosphere</h3>
        <br />
        <p> After many decades and many scientific breakthroughs, we have achieved natural atmosphere on Mars!</p>
      </div>

      <div class="col-12 col-sm">
        <h3>Community</h3>
        <br />
        <p> Connected by the vision of a less populated, less polluted world - the New Martian Community is a chance to start fresh. Come, be amongst friends.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

   
   
  

    <div class="row">
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg"><i class="fas fa-rocket"></i><p class="text-center">I'm ready to be a Martian. Take me to Mars</p></button>  
    </div>










    <% if notice.present? %>
      <p class="alert alert-info"><%= notice %></p>
    <% end %>
    <% if alert.present? %>
        <p class="alert alert-danger"><%= alert %></p>
    <% end %>

    <%= yield %>
  </body>
</html>
